dc_title_s: Map of Western Florida showing the lands held by the Michigan Syndicate; Michigan Syndicate; A. L. Langellier, general agent, Pensacola, Fla.
dc_description_s: Under glued strip "Louisville and Nashville Railroad Company, The vacant Government Lands subject to Homestead entry in Western Florida 1898." 1 map: col.; 67 x 125 cm This map is in the public domain.
